{"tid":1113081,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"挑機","createTime":"2019-04-17T18:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T19:00:26.000Z","uid":249119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a7e4d9005eddd109bde706f5eb360b1aefeac2","tid":1113081,"uid":249119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:35:16.000Z","msg":"今日見到有人分享咗景三嘅《香港重建計劃》<br />\n見到佢用city skyline整咗一個香港出嚟<br />\n稍為睇咗佢嘅YouTube 都整得唔錯<br />\n不過建築、道路、地圖比例就唔係畫得幾好啦<br />\n<br />\n大約幾個月前 我整咗個1:1香港<br />\n花咗好多時間一直喺度整 見到景三嘅《香港重建計劃》我就想同大家分享下我整出尼嘅香港<br />\n道路建築位置、街道同埋地圖大多數都係跟足比例去整 宜家諗返嗰陣時正真係一啲都唔容易 花咗好多好多時間<br />\n <br />\n以下係我整嗰個香港嘅相！<br />\n希望大家鍾意啦<br />\n尼啲先叫做真正嘅用遊戲整嘅香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LESFUb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLESFUb5.jpg&h=0bcd12db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REztiDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREztiDM.jpg&h=afeb7b39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Tsbgqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Tsbgqs.jpg&h=345d70da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAcKBqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAcKBqt.jpg&h=43d07719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ey0wgqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fey0wgqu.jpg&h=93c205ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AA5PNxa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAA5PNxa.jpg&h=ca6e80ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGvwgqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGvwgqx.jpg&h=9dfc93ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwGWsxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwGWsxd.jpg&h=974e5138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://